#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/testing/_private/utils.py:docstring
#: of numpy.testing._private.utils.assert_allclose:67
msgid ""
"When one of `actual` and `desired` is a scalar and the other is array_like, "
"the function performs the comparison as if the scalar were broadcasted to "
"the shape of the array. Note that empty arrays are therefore considered "
"equal to scalars. This behaviour can be disabled by setting ``strict==True``."
msgstr ""

