#: of numpy.testing._private.utils.assert_allclose:83
msgid ""
"As mentioned in the Notes section, `assert_allclose` has special handling "
"for scalars. Here, the test checks that the value of `numpy.sin` is nearly "
"zero at integer multiples of π."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/testing/_private/utils.py:docstring
